Eileen Ryan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eileen_Ryan 0 Eileen Ryan (née Annucci; born October 16, 1928) is an American actress who has appeared in a number of movies and TV series. She is the widow of actor and director Leo Penn, and mother of actors Sean Penn and Chris Penn and singer Michael Penn.
